#: ../effects.rst:374
msgid "tracking"
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:374
msgid "``(float, 0–1)`` Horizontal **line wobble** plus a subtle bottom **skew**. Higher values increase amplitude and skew height."
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:375
msgid "bleed"
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:375
msgid "``(float, 0–1)`` **Chroma bleed / fringing.** Horizontal chroma shift + blur with a slight desaturation. Gives the “rainbow edge” look."
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:376
msgid "softness"
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:376
msgid "``(float, 0–1)`` **Luma softness.** Small horizontal blur on Y (approx. 0–2 px). Keep low to retain detail when noise is high."
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:377
msgid "noise"
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:377
msgid "``(float, 0–1)`` **Snow, hiss, and dropouts.** Controls grain strength, probability/length of white **streaks**, and a faint line hum."
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:378
msgid "stripe"
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:378
msgid "``(float, 0–1)`` **Tracking stripe.** Lifts the bottom band, adds hiss/noise there, and widens the lifted region as the value increases."
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:379
msgid "static_bands"
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:379
msgid "``(float, 0–1)`` **Static bursts.** Short bright bands with **row-clumped streaks** (many “shooting stars” across neighboring rows)."
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:380
msgid "seed_offset"
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:380
msgid "``(int, 0–1000)`` Adds to the internal seed (derived from the effect ID) for deterministic variation between clips."
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:383
#: ../effects.rst:1070
msgid "**Usage notes**"
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:385
msgid "**Subtle “home video”**: ``tracking=0.25``, ``bleed=0.20``, ``softness=0.20``, ``noise=0.25``, ``stripe=0.10``, ``static_bands=0.05``."
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:386
msgid "**Bad tracking / head clog**: ``tracking=0.8–1.0``, ``stripe=0.6–0.9``, ``noise=0.6–0.8``, ``static_bands=0.4–0.6``, ``softness<=0.2``, and set ``bleed`` to about 0.3."
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:387
msgid "**Color fringing only**: raise ``bleed`` (about 0.5) and keep other controls low."
msgstr ""

#: ../effects.rst:388
